				                <div>Hello Grant,<br />
<br />
To be able to toggle mobile site to classic site you would need a bit of javascript involved as well. The javascript would set a session cookie for you while the htaccess code would evaluate that cookie to determine which version of the site to display.<br />
<br />
The htaccess would need to add a rewrite condition in order to handle the cookie option:<br />
<div class="code_block">RewriteCond %{HTTP_COOKIE} !^.*user_id=1   [NC]</div><br />
<br />
Kindest Regards,<br />
