<p>deny from all</p>
<p>&lt;/Limit&gt;</p>
<p>AuthName 1777americanainn.com</p>
<p>AuthUserFile /home/amer1x/public_html/_vti_pvt/service.pwd</p>
<p>AuthGroupFile /home/amer1x/public_html/_vti_pvt/service.grp</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
